ebchat"},"updatedAt":1776175758486,"sessionId":"92922f70-a2f7-462a-9935-b4b6c316158b","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44910,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776175757764,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/92922f70-a2f7-462a-9935-b4b6c316158b.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7 5p Progress Report — AHV Works] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 2:09 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 14:09 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776175757764,"__openclaw":{"id":"609a5710","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions_list and the heartbeat-state.json file to compare current state against last known state."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gque4bjega14_1","name":"session